data.title: Pampanga
data.meta_description:
Pampanga - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides an overview of Pampanga province in the Philippines, including its:

- Geography and location within the country 
- Rich history dating back to pre-colonial times and its role in independence movements
- Cultural sites, customs, and festivals that showcase the native Kapampangan people's heritage
- Predominantly Catholic religious traditions that are central to community life and ceremonies
